## 3. Backend API Reference

**Base URL:** `https://traindiary-refactor-backend.vercel.app/api`  
**Auth:** Bearer JWT token in `Authorization` header  
**Response format:** All responses are `{ success: boolean, data: T, message?: string }`

### 3.1 Authentication Endpoints

| Method | Path | Payload | Notes |
|---|---|---|---|
| `POST` | `/auth/login` | `{ email, password }` | Returns `{ token, user }` |
| `POST` | `/auth/signup` | `{ fullname, email, password, phone }` | Sends verification email |
| `POST` | `/auth/verify` | `{ token }` | Email verification |
| `POST` | `/auth/forgot-password` | `{ email }` | Password reset request |

**Login response `data` shape:**
```json
{
  "token": "JWT_STRING",
  "user": { "user_id": 1, "id": 1, "username": "...", "email": "..." }
}
```

**Token storage:** In RN, use `expo-secure-store` instead of `localStorage`. Token key: `"auth_token"`, User key: `"auth_user"`.

### 3.2 Users

| Method | Path | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/users` | Fetch current authenticated user |

### 3.3 Nutrition — Metrics (Body Specs)

| Method | Path | Payload | Notes |
|---|---|---|---|
| `POST` | `/nutrition/metrics` | `MetricData` | Save user body specs |
| `GET` | `/nutrition/metrics/latest` | — | Fetch latest recorded metrics |

**`MetricData` shape:**
```ts
{
  age: number;
  sex: "male" | "female";
  height_cm: number;
  weight_kg: number;
  body_fat_percentage?: number; // optional
  activity_level: "sedentary" | "light" | "moderate" | "heavy" | "athlete";
}
```

### 3.4 Nutrition — Goals

| Method | Path | Payload | Notes |
|---|---|---|---|
| `POST` | `/nutrition/goals` | `GoalCalculationParams` | Calculate & save nutrition goal |
| `GET` | `/nutrition/goals` | — | Fetch current goal |
| `POST` | `/nutrition/goals/calculate` | `GoalCalculationParams` | Preview calculated goal without saving |

**`GoalCalculationParams` shape:**
```ts
{
  age: number;
  sex: "male" | "female";
  height_cm: number;
  weight_kg: number;
  body_fat_percentage?: number;
  activity_level: "sedentary" | "light" | "moderate" | "heavy" | "athlete";
  goal_type: "cutting" | "lean_bulk" | "maintain" | "recomposition";
  goal_speed: "slow" | "moderate" | "aggressive";
  target_weight_kg: number;
  workout_type: "strength" | "cardio" | "mixed";
}
```

### 3.5 Nutrition — Meals

| Method | Path | Payload | Notes |
|---|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/meals?month=YYYY-MM` | — | Fetch all meals for a month |
| `POST` | `/meals` | `{ meal_type, log_date, items[] }` | Create meal with food items |
| `DELETE` | `/meals/:meal_id` | — | Delete a meal |
| `GET` | `/foods?updated_after=ISO` | — | Fetch food list (incremental sync) |

**Meal types:** `"breakfast"`, `"lunch"`, `"dinner"`, `"snack"`

**Food item in create payload:**
```ts
{ food_id: number; numbers_of_serving: number }
```

### 3.6 Nutrition — Water / Hydration

| Method | Path | Payload | Notes |
|---|---|---|---|
| `POST` | `/nutrition/water` | `{ amount_ml, log_date }` | Log water intake |
| `GET` | `/nutrition/water?date=YYYY-MM-DD` | — | Fetch daily water total + goal |

### 3.7 Workouts

| Method | Path | Payload | Notes |
|---|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/workouts?month=YYYY-MM` | — | Fetch sessions for a month |
| `POST` | `/workouts` | `{ scheduled_date, type?, notes? }` | Create new session |
| `GET` | `/workouts/:session_id` | — | Fetch session details |
| `PATCH` | `/workouts/:session_id/complete` | — | Mark session as COMPLETED |
| `DELETE` | `/workouts/:session_id` | — | Delete session |
| `GET` | `/exercises?updated_after=ISO` | — | Fetch exercise list (incremental sync) |

**Session `status` values:** `"IN_PROGRESS"`, `"COMPLETED"`

**Session detail / exercise log endpoints:**
| Method | Path | Payload |
|---|---|---|
| `POST` | `/workouts/:session_id/details` | `{ exercise_id, planned_sets, planned_reps }` |
| `DELETE` | `/workouts/:session_id/details/:detail_id` | — |
| `POST` | `/workouts/:session_id/details/:detail_id/logs` | `{ reps, weight_kg, notes? }` |
| `PATCH` | `/workouts/logs/:set_id` | `{ reps?, weight_kg?, status? }` |
| `DELETE` | `/workouts/logs/:set_id` | — |
| `POST` | `/workouts/logs/sync` | `{ updates: [{set_id, reps, weight_kg, status}] }` | Bulk sync |
| `POST` | `/workouts/:session_id/planned-exercises` | `{ exercises: [{exercise_id, planned_sets, planned_reps}] }` |

### 3.8 Progress & Summary

| Method | Path | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/progress` | Fetch workout progress data |
| `GET` | `/summary?month=YYYY-MM` | Monthly summary — workouts, nutrition, hydration, GR score, muscle split |

**Summary response includes:**
- `total_workouts`, `gr_score`, `gr_score_change`, `longest_streak`
- `muscle_split: [{name, value}]` — percentages by muscle group
- `daily_data: [{date, workouts, kcal, protein, carbs, fats, fiber, sugar, gr, water}]`
- `calories_avg`, `protein_avg`, `carbs_avg`, `fats_avg`
- `exercise_data: [{name, count, volume, history:[{date, weight, reps}]}]`

### 3.9 Programs (Workout Plans)

| Method | Path | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/programs` | List available workout programs (plans) |
| `POST` | `/programs/:plan_id/start` | Start a workout plan |

### 3.10 AI Chat

Endpoint: `POST /ai/...` (streaming AI assistant — lower priority for RN port)

