| `users` | `user_id`, `email`, `username`, `verified` |
| `user_metrics` | `metric_id` (IDENTITY), `user_id`, `age`, `sex`, `height_cm`, `weight_kg`, `body_fat_percentage`, `activity_level`, `recorded_at` |
| `nutrition_goals` | `goal_id` (IDENTITY), `user_id`, `calories_target`, `protein_target_g`, `carbs_target_g`, `fat_target_g`, `hydration_target_ml`, `goal_type`, `goal_speed` |
| `user_meals` | `meal_id`, `user_id`, `meal_type`, `log_date` |
| `user_meal_details` | `meal_detail_id`, `meal_id`, `food_id`, `numbers_of_serving` |
| `foods` | `food_id`, `name`, `calories_per_serving`, `protein_per_serving`, `carbs_per_serving`, `fat_per_serving`, many micronutrient columns, `updated_at` |
| `water_logs` | `water_log_id` (IDENTITY), `user_id`, `amount_ml`, `log_date` |
| `workout_sessions` | `session_id`, `user_id`, `scheduled_date`, `type`, `status`, `gr_score` |
| `session_details` | `session_detail_id`, `session_id`, `exercise_id` |
| `sessions_exercise_details` | `set_id`, `session_detail_id`, `reps`, `weight_kg`, `notes`, `status` |
| `exercises` | `exercise_id`, `name`, `category`, `default_sets`, `default_reps`, `difficulty_factor`, `type`, `updated_at` |
| `personal_records` | `record_id` (IDENTITY), `user_id`, `exercise_id`, `weight_kg`, `achieved_at` |
| `workout_plans` | `plan_id`, `name`, `description` |
| `plan_days` | `plan_day_id`, `plan_id`, `day_number`, `day_type` |
| `plan_day_exercises` | `plan_day_exercise_id`, `plan_day_id`, `exercise_id`, `sets`, `reps` |

