## 9. Recommended React Native Tech Stack

```
Expo SDK (latest) — Managed workflow
expo-router          — File-based navigation (mirrors Next.js structure)
expo-secure-store    — Secure token storage (replaces localStorage)
axios or fetch       — HTTP client (keep same API layer logic, swap localStorage → AsyncStorage)
react-native-reanimated — Animations (replaces framer-motion)
react-native-gesture-handler — Gestures
@shopify/react-native-skia OR victory-native — Charts (replace recharts/shadcn charts)
@gorhom/bottom-sheet — Bottom sheet modals (replaces web Modal components)
react-native-safe-area-context — Safe area handling
expo-font            — Space Grotesk + Inter fonts (same as web)
@tanstack/react-query — Server state management (strongly recommend adding this)
zustand              — Client/local state (replace useState-heavy pages)
```

> **Navigation structure suggestion using expo-router:**
> ```
> app/
>   (auth)/
>     signin.tsx
>     signup.tsx
>     verify-email.tsx
>     forgot-password.tsx
>   (app)/
>     _layout.tsx         ← Tab navigator (matches FloatingNav)
>     index.tsx           ← Home/Landing
>     workout/
>       index.tsx
>       [sessionId].tsx   ← Workout details
>     nutrition/
>       index.tsx
>     summary/
>       index.tsx
>     programs/
>       index.tsx
>     profile/
>       index.tsx
> ```

